The paper deals with the problem of online deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The focus is on image recognition tasks, which suggests that the paper could belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep neural networks and ensemble learning techniques suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the use of memory architectures and transfer learning techniques suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
